    {
      "id": "after-mapping",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 500,
      "y": 590,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "Key Mapping (AFTER):\n─────────────────────────────\nK1 → Server A  ✓ unchanged\nK2 → Server B  ✓ unchanged\nK3 → Server E  ⚡ MOVED!\nK4 → Server D  ✓ unchanged\nK5 → Server A  ✓ unchanged",
